HEADWORD: Pseudonym
<hw>Pseu"do*nym</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>pseudonyme</ets>. See <er>Pseudonymous</er>.]</ety> <def>A
fictitious name assumed for the time, as by an author; a pen name; an
alias.</def> <altsp>[Written also <asp>pseudonyme</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pseudonymity</ent>⟦br⟧
